name: OBJKT history (reloaded)
description: This is an updated version of OBJKT#25459, that sadly stopped working. Type the OBJKT number and you will get all the associated transactions since the moment it was minted. OBJKTs with a lot of transactions might take time to load, so be patient. Note that this tool depends on API calls and it might break in the future. Creator: Javier Gracia Carpio | @jagracar
